  "title": "Python 新版本去 GIL 刷屏，Karpathy 点赞敢死队，Python 之父：冷静，别神话并发",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&mid=2247646785&idx=2&sn=dd41afd9d0122aff95619c0980249d47",
  "date": "2025-10-19 05:31:00",
